title: NFL coaching rumors with Brady Quinn (Football 1/03)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn to break down the latest coaching rumors and NFL news, including how Miami and Adam Gase split ways and whether he can get another job this offseason (4:00), whether Zac Taylor can land a head coaching job at the age of 35 (11:00), debating the Buccaneers vs. Dolphins job (19:30), if Pat Fitzgerald might be willing to leave Northwestern for an NFL job (23:00), Kliff Kingsbury's viability as a head coach (26:00), Wild Card Weekend New Year's Resolutions (30:30) and the Antonio Brown situation in Pittsburgh (46:30).
